Cashier: what does he do????
	1. charge(Item...args) // charges customer 
	2. order(Item...args) // orders item for customer request
	3. openCashRegister() // makes line available for customers to come
	4. closeCashRegister() // make line unavailable
Tutor:
	1. guideCustomer(String request) - guides Customer to requested section

SalesMan:
	1. convincePotentialCustomer(String phoneNumber) //void: random chance to get new customer
  2. convinceCustomerToBuy(String phonenumber) // 
Chef:
	1. Cook methods - set of actions to cook request food
	2. claimReady(Food...args) - announces to the cashier the food is ready for serving
